# Consistency

- Commits follow Conventional Commits: feat/fix/docs/test/refactor/chore
- Rust naming: snake_case for functions/variables, PascalCase for types
- TypeScript naming: camelCase for functions/variables, PascalCase for components/types
- File naming: snake_case for Rust, PascalCase for React components, camelCase for TS utilities
- All errors must be typed — no string errors or anyhow in library crates
